snippet.title: Spiritlands [GL Trailer- Alpha]
snippet.description:
Manage, Explore, Gather, Research, Build, Automate.

The Greenlight trailer for 4X strategy game- Spiritlands! A show of the main Alpha features, with a lot more being added all the time.
